{"tid":450358,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"連登有無人識「一個快樂的傳說」（美麗人生）","createTime":"2017-10-28T06:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T12:42:55.000Z","uid":12628,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9dd2de8afd8682fa425496855dc3bdc664851e","tid":450358,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:16:52.000Z","msg":"《美麗人生》（意大利語：La vita &egrave; bella，意為「人生是美好」），1997年電影，由導演羅貝托&middot;貝尼尼自編自演，榮獲奧斯卡最佳男主角、欧洲电影奖最佳影片及多個國際大奬。電影講述意大利一對猶太父子被送進納粹集中營，父親Guido Orefice（導演羅貝托&middot;貝尼尼飾）不忍年僅五歲的兒子飽受驚恐，利用自己豐富的想像力扯謊說他們正身處一個遊戲當中，必須接受集中營中種種規矩以換得分數贏取最後大奬。影片笑中有淚，將一個大時代小人物的故事，轉化為一個扣人心弦的悲喜劇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/141631_808b378ef47a0d9fa840c015d1deaf46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F141631_808b378ef47a0d9fa840c015d1deaf46.jpg&h=f407be27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/141649_5b75ea4e06da8b1d04f7bf4742389c7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F141649_5b75ea4e06da8b1d04f7bf4742389c7d.jpg&h=9c3087b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d889ad766bcf588984782bc98c1182716c789127","tid":450358,"uid":75394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ad1475721c869622a9b672e2a43576a6aaa099","tid":450358,"uid":62379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:21:19.000Z","msg":"都依家都唔明個軍醫點解唔救佢哋"},{"pid":"c98b0c38e995e511c3f0e7b7d3072bafd571a6bb","tid":450358,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:21:19.000Z","msg":"睇親都好感動，男主角樂觀嘅性格，雖然改變唔到大環境，但心靈嘅樂觀同正面態度，往往令困境有一絲希望。<br />\n以喜劇角度演繹一出悲劇，呢套野真係無愧拎咁個最佳電影！"},{"pid":"f23afda712559211fbc2aa8de4dacbabc56cfb88","tid":450358,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"