\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個軍醫心地幾好，而且同個男主角有交情，但最多都係盡量令佢唔好咁早比人殺，唔可能救到佢地出生天"},{"pid":"e13fca9ee01eefa7baee691e77b765677a40d827","tid":450358,"uid":74727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:43:21.000Z","msg":"印象中好似最後個細佬喺個櫃入面 個呀爸俾人捉住咗要死 臨死經過個櫃嗰時 個呀爸仲要扮好笑咁行路等個仔繼續以為係遊戲 睇到呢到都喊到停唔到"},{"pid":"c5f6a98e2738d533dadc1859dda94d267c7f000b","tid":450358,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:51:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>印象中好似最後個細佬喺個櫃入面 個呀爸俾人捉住咗要死 臨死經過個櫃嗰時 個呀爸仲要扮好笑咁行路等個仔繼續以為係遊戲 睇到呢到都喊到停唔到</blockquote><br />\n係，最後果細路見到部雪曼坦克，真係以為自己贏左遊戲，仲見返佢阿媽"},{"pid":"9b72d315f7b4979e96988e288d7f129993ba9ca5","tid":450358,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"grazie --&gt; danke<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece7b253b9b180651960c57fcbbfcf795b650b70","tid":450358,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T08:25:45.000Z","msg":"係連登講啲正面嘅野發覺自己有啲岸鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aea3996b603efd4922469d1ee51b1ab572007f8","tid":450358,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T08:32:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係連登講啲正面嘅野發覺自己有啲岸鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登有D廢老會屌人睇舊戲吹奏舊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6740664388b2527ff08e405338e657e50797cc3","tid":450358,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T09:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係連登講啲正面嘅野發覺自己有啲岸鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登有D廢老會屌人睇舊戲吹奏舊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇珠光寶氣果啲仲舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過舊